        <item>
            <title>Meta 放棄與 Apple Vision Pro 競爭，轉移重心開發低成本 VR 裝置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:30:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[La Jolla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Meta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vr]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258883</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">根據 The Information 的報道，Meta 正計劃取消開發與 Apple Vision Pro 直接競爭的高階頭戴式 VR 裝置，由於其代號為 La Jolla 的高階頭戴式 VR 裝置所需的 Micro OLED 屏幕成本過於高昂，未來將轉移重心至開發低成本的 VR 裝置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1258902 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/applevisionprovsmeta-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/applevisionprovsmeta-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/applevisionprovsmeta.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.roadtovr.com/meta-quest-3-apple-vision-pro-resolution-resolving-power-display-quality/">Road to VR</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Meta 原本的計劃是將高階頭戴式 VR 裝置 La Jolla 於 2027 年推出並與 Apple 的 Vision Pro 直接競爭，並將其定價於 1000 美元以下。消息指出 La Jolla 為了使用與 Vision Pro 相同的顯示技術而採用了更昂貴的 Micro OLED 屏幕，但成本實在太高而正式取消開發高階頭戴式 VR 裝置的計劃。Meta 的首席技術總監 Andrew Bosworth 亦在 Threads 上暗示了這個決定，他表示一直在研究多個原型機，但不是每一個都會投入生產，某些項目被放棄的情況經常會出現。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1258886 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meta-694x318.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="318" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meta-694x318.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meta.jpg 1222w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@boztank/post/C_BS8BuPfQZ">Threads @boztank</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Meta 之前推出的高階頭戴式 VR 裝置 Quest Pro 未有得到市場強烈的迴響，其雖然以「高階」產品作推廣，但仍然使用低階的 LCD 屏幕。雖暫不打算繼續開發高階市場，Meta 仍然會全力開發低階至中階的頭戴式 VR 裝置，其中包括預計會在 2026 年推出的 Quest 4，而 9 月將有機會推出 Quest 3 的新版本作為加入 Meta 生態系統的入門裝置，價格約為 300-400 美元並有機會將其命名為 Quest 3S。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.flatpanelshd.com/news.php?subaction=showfull&amp;id=1724655513&amp;fbclid=IwY2xjawE6gDxleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHSM0fO-BQxwWbEWMRGsTYvyJ6_DGIACYhEzPe4McYbIkLl51XDbKtMdUNw_aem_PI5M2mufbGuMGGDe-HpkXA">FlatpanelsHD</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://appleinsider.com/inside/apple-vision-pro/vs/apple-vision-pro-vs-meta-quest-heatsets---how-the-approaches-compare">AppleInsider</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/apple-vision-pro-preorder-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Apple Vision Pro 香港預訂教學　戴眼鏡也能輕鬆買 + 臉部掃描過程</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/taobao-xiaomi-vision-pro-trial-su7-car/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">安坐家中 Vision Pro 雲端試車　淘寶小米合作推虛擬小米 SU7 試車體驗</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/aic-warns-hkgov/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Google、Amazon、Meta 向香港發出警告，憂基建電腦安全立法影響網絡供應商誠信</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/">Meta 放棄與 Apple Vision Pro 競爭，轉移重心開發低成本 VR 裝置</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>全新 Porsche 電動 Macan 香港預覽   800V 架構快速充電 + 可配氣壓避震及後輪轉向</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/porsche-macanev-800v/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=porsche-macanev-800v</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/porsche-macanev-800v/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Macan 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Macan Turbo EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Porsche Macan Electric]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258790</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新 Porsche Macan Electric 純電動 SUV 最近正式於灣仔保時捷旗艦店進行閉門預覽，場中展出了包括 Macan 4 及 Macan Turbo 兩款全新電動 SUV，預計廠方將於 10 月正式推出，最快可於今年第四季交付。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258853" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112722-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112722-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112722.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112757-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112757-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112757.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Macan Turbo EV</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112942-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112942-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112942.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113121-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113121-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113121.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Macan 4</p><p>場中展出的兩款新車均屬香港規格的右軚版本，新車採用了全新的 Porsche PPE（Premium Platform Electric）800V 充電架構，當使用 800V 充電站時 DC 直流快充效率可高達 270kW，並於 21 分鐘將電池電量由 10% 充至 80%。兩款新車型號均配備 100kWh 鋰電池，前後雙馬達組成的 4WD 系統， Macan 4 標準版馬力為 408 匹、650Nm 扭力，0-100km/h 加速為 5.2 秒，續航力為 613 公里 (WLTP)。而高級版 Macan Turbo 馬力達 639 匹，最高扭力為 1,130Nm，0-100km/h 加速只需 3.3 秒，續航力為 591 公里 (WLTP)。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113210-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113210-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113210.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112710-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112710-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112710.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_1125430-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_1125430-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_1125430.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112902-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112902-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/up