ontent/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112916-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112916-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112916.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Macan Turbo EV</p><p>全新 Macan EV 採用了分離式 LED 矩陣式頭燈，車窗亦採用綫條更簡潔利落的無邊框車窗，全新主動式空氣力學套件 (PAA) 及新設計的擾流裝置令 Macan EV 風阻系數只有 0.25Cd。內籠方面，新車採用 12.6 吋懸浮式曲面數碼化錶板，整合通訊功能的 10.9 吋中央螢幕及可選配的 10.9 吋乘客螢幕及 HUD 投射功能。新車暫定售價為: Macan 4 ($1,048,000) / Macan Turbo ($1,448,000)。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112455-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112455-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112455.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112405-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112405-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112405.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113139-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113139-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113139.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258878